{"id": 2552, "genre": 1001, "title": "看剧时，你都有过哪些“这样拍说不定很好看”的脑洞？", "description": "一些“如果我是导演我就会这样拍”的奇思妙想。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 4684, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201810081649262AXyZb18InpVBdsz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 304641, "content": "喜欢女主的令人心疼的男二有个好结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473426}, {"id": 304642, "content": "剧情不够就不够，不要用回忆凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473426}, {"id": 304643, "content": "打破套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473426}, {"id": 305411, "content": "给反派的角色设计添一些人性极端或微小之善", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440096}, {"id": 304645, "content": "让主角历经千辛万苦，克服种种困难，打败各个大小\"反派\"，\"拯救世界\"之后，突然发现原来所谓的反派才是一直在努力拯救世界，而自己才是这个世界最大的威胁...", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867637}, {"id": 304901, "content": "主角没有主角光环", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474378}, {"id": 307205, "content": "剧情什么的，人物的什么的，全丢掉。光看背景也很不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427152}, {"id": 304646, "content": "请告诉我坏人是怎么变坏的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275723}, {"id": 304647, "content": "音乐别那么煽情，求求你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473455}, {"id": 305931, "content": "主角在被道德绑架的时候直接diss道：我对其他人都很好 但就是很讨厌你 对不起对不起这绝对是我的问题 但是没办法 就是讨厌你  可是我对其他人都很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479134}, {"id": 311307, "content": "大雄用任意门去静香家，每次刚好静香在拉肚子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182031}, {"id": 304652, "content": "请一定要对反派补枪多次", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473483}, {"id": 304653, "content": "主角在撒谎的时候一定能被看穿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473499}, {"id": 305677, "content": "主角跳崖，果不其然死了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435785}, {"id": 304658, "content": "能不能把反派出现的定式BGM换换🔇", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298385}, {"id": 304659, "content": "每个剧的主角都挺帅，来一个不帅的撒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460104}, {"id": 311315, "content": "娱乐圈中女主通过被金主潜规则一路上位，上位成功后踢掉金主不断提高自己成为影视公司老板，在床上成为了公司旗下小鲜肉需要讨好的金主。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498034}, {"id": 304661, "content": "女主不倒贴独立自主自强不墨迹不傻白甜，男主作就干他丫的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456423}, {"id": 304669, "content": "战争片看照片的不会死(￢_￢)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468279}, {"id": 304671, "content": "“我们今天在这里义结金兰/拜把子好吗”\n“不了不了”\n全剧终", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473674}, {"id": 304672, "content": "女生救王子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244859}, {"id": 304932, "content": "角色全员智商在线，情节紧凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113177}, {"id": 305453, "content": "如果爱情小说中的傻白甜主角一直是隐藏的心机女（故事要像推理小说一样发展，这样谁也不知道），故事将会非常精彩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476284}, {"id": 304686, "content": "反派不墨迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1452453}, {"id": 304687, "content": "放第一集留着全部大悬念  直接全剧终 😊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473709}, {"id": 304943, "content": "当反派派人谋害主角时，例如开车撞重要证人，都会被交警或红绿灯挡住，失去了最好时机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771207}, {"id": 312367, "content": "男主喜欢女主就说出来嘛！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844161}, {"id": 304688, "content": "主角经历了一系列挫折、失败，屡战屡败，屡败屡战，终于输得彻彻底底，内裤也没剩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253166}, {"id": 304689, "content": "全是配角没主角\n和生活一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 307249, "content": "主角被害能不能直接还回去？别婆婆妈妈等nm的蜕变。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478404}, {"id": 304690, "content": "吊丝与女神经历风雨\n最后\n女神嫁给了高富帅\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473733}, {"id": 304694, "content": "女主是女神，遗世独立，冰清玉洁，和男主分别多年后，嫁给了其他人。见到男主的第一句话:我以为你死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473667}, {"id": 304698, "content": "黑暗骑士换个女主就完美了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139320}, {"id": 304701, "content": "大反派一开始就和主角斗个你死我活，不分出胜负决不罢休，全剧完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473795}, {"id": 304702, "content": "事实证明，权力的游戏是反套路的盛宴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928475}, {"id": 302655, "content": "女扮男装的女主角被男主角一眼识破", "image": null, "praise_count": 325, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302656, "content": "出现误会，一方马上解释，另一方认真倾听，问题瞬间解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 573, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302657, "content": "反派从不负责解释剧情，直接一枪干掉主角", "image": null, "praise_count": 824, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302658, "content": "男女主角掉落悬崖之后脸先着地", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 304709, "content": "慢慢的已经无法看完整的电视剧了，通常看十分钟评论9分钟，一分钟看服饰。现在看纪录片多余其他。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379229}, {"id": 305742, "content": "好人坏人不是一眼就能看出来，有大反转的那种剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478009}, {"id": 305755, "content": "反派死之前别tm回忆了好吗 输了就是输了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474808}, {"id": 304738, "content": "时臣不再背锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198461}, {"id": 304483, "content": "把80集电视剧还原回8集。", "image": null, "praise_count": 396, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 304484, "content": "男主识🍵功能满级", "image": null, "praise_count": 111, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472844}, {"id": 304486, "content": "女主被绑over，此剧完", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472845}, {"id": 304487, "content": "主角一做死就会死。没什么光环加持，这样他才能好好活着", "image": "img/option/option/20181016110838bPuycdqt7CnOwJMz.jpg", "praise_count": 426, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429465}, {"id": 304488, "content": "女主洗澡，男主闯不进去，门栓着呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472851}, {"id": 304745, "content": "星矢的小宇宙最终没有再次爆发，射手座圣衣也没有出来保护他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435424}, {"id": 304746, "content": "反派从开头到结尾一言不发，营造出一种神秘莫测的感觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473763}]}